summary: All Weapons for Ebony with Gold Ornaments and many little Changes

Modified SkyrimPrefy.ini + FXAA: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=450
Ebony Armor Female: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=493
